sql: SELECT count(DISTINCT(`authors`.`id`)) AS `count` FROM `authors` AS `authors` LEFT OUTER JOIN `books` AS `books` ON `authors`.`id` = `books`.`authors_id` INNER JOIN `publishers_books` AS `books.publishers_books` ON `books`.`id` = `books.publishers_books`.`books_id` WHERE (`authors`.`id` >= 0 AND `authors`.`id` < 10) AND (`authors`.`name` != 'Bob' OR `authors`.`name` != 'Alice')
